Wichita.Wichita Southeast High School: Wichita Southeast High School, known locally as Southeast, is a fully accredited urban high school, serving students in grades 9-12, located in Wichita, Kansas. The school is within the Unified School District 259. Wichita High School Southeast is one of many high schools located within the city limits of Wichita, KS. The official school colors are gold and black.
